@wp.kernel
def vec_kiorkl(pos: wp.array(dtype=wp.vec3), vel: wp.array(dtype=wp.vec3), acc: wp.array(dtype=wp.vec3)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    dt = 7.16
    new_vel = vel[tid] + acc[tid] * dt
    pos[tid] = pos[tid] + new_vel * dt
    vel[tid] = new_vel
